        "text": "Customize your closed captions\n\nTo customize the way your closed captions appear on Windows 10:\n\nOn a Windows 10 PC, go to Settings.\n\nTap or clickEase of Access.\n\nTap or click Closed captions.\n\nCustomize how closed captions will be displayed on your screens.\n\nNote Your changes will be reflected in the Preview pane at the top of the window as you make them.\n\nYou can customize the following settings:\n\nFont\n\nCaption color\n\nCaption transparency\n\nCaption style\n\nCaption size\n\nCaption effects\n\nBackground and window\n\nBackground color\n\nBackground transparency\n\nWindow color\n\nWindow transparency"
